snippet.title: Chocolate Factory - Official Release Date Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Dive into the colorful world of Chocolate Factory and take another look at this upcoming first-person factory automation game featuring a little exploration and combat. Chocolate Factory will be available on PC on June 18, 2024. Build your dream Chocolate Factory among candy cane forests and gumdrop hills to produce the tastiest sweets.
